## SECTION 3: REGISTRATION & PAYMENTS
(Seat Control - Invoices - Confirmation)

### 1. Seat Control
- [ ] Confirm remaining seats count
- [ ] Define seat-hold rules:
  - [ ] hold duration
  - [ ] what "hold" requires (deposit or not)
  - [ ] expiration process

### 2. Invoice & Payment
- [ ] Issue invoice with correct course date + doctor name
- [ ] Confirm payment method
- [ ] Confirm payment received (receipt/proof)
- [ ] Record transaction reference (Stripe ID / wire confirmation)

### 3. Policy Acknowledgment
- [ ] Doctor has received refund/cancellation policy
- [ ] Doctor acknowledges policy (email reply is enough if needed)

### 4. Confirmation Status
- [ ] Mark as "Paid"
- [ ] Mark as "Confirmed"
- [ ] Add to course roster

### 5. Comms Cadence (Minimal)
- [ ] Confirmation message
- [ ] 7-day reminder
- [ ] 48-hour logistics reminder
- [ ] Day-of travel check-in

