## SECTION 6: POST-COURSE WRAP-UP & CE COMPLIANCE
(Certificates - Evaluations - Records)

### 1. Completion Verification
- [ ] Final attendance confirmed by day
- [ ] CE hours calculated based on actual schedule

### 2. Evaluations
- [ ] Course evaluation distributed
- [ ] Collect responses (store in course folder)

### 3. Certificates
- [ ] Generate CE certificates with:
  - [ ] doctor name
  - [ ] course title
  - [ ] dates
  - [ ] CE hours
  - [ ] provider statement (as required)
- [ ] Deliver certificates (email or portal)
- [ ] Save copy in records folder

### 4. Compliance Archive (PACE-ready)
- [ ] Final agenda / schedule
- [ ] Learning objectives
- [ ] Faculty CV/bios (CE-appropriate)
- [ ] Attendance log
- [ ] Evaluations summary
- [ ] Provider statements / disclosures as required

### 5. Post-Course Follow-Up (Operational)
- [ ] Thank-you message (professional)
- [ ] Invite to alumni channel (if used)
- [ ] Capture internal improvements list for next cohort

